" Dependency for Rails Vim
execute pathogen#infect()

" Make my vim beautiful and functional
syntax on
set shiftwidth=2
set tabstop=2
set showmatch
set autoindent 
set smartindent
set smarttab
set noerrorbells
set number
set ruler
set scrolloff=5
set sidescrolloff=5

" Alias commands because I like to hold down shift too much
:command WQ wq
:command Wq wq
:command W w
:command Q q
